{"tid":911013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉迺強：港人血液有水貨基因","createTime":"2018-11-21T14:43:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T02:28:47.000Z","uid":70786,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"af5c2eea36a8d27d9ca7adcc1df89a40e4e0ed70","tid":911013,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:43:15.000Z","msg":"一簽多行若收緊至一周一行，外界預料水貨活動將大受打擊，但基本法委員會委員劉迺強卻指，水貨問題亦不能因此遏止，因香港人血液中有「水貨基因」，水貨市場將由港人壟斷。<br />\n劉迺強昨日出席基本法25周年法律研討會時發言指出，水貨問題不會因為一周一行而停止，「<span style=\"color: red;\">你唔好呃自己，我哋（香港人）有成百年（走水貨）傳統喺度，我哋香港人嘅血裏面已經流住水貨嘅因子、嘅基因喺度」，認為港人終會壟斷水貨市場。</span><br />\n他又指一周一行是向惡勢力屈服，令參加光復行動的人以為「自己好嘢」，若要求對等，港人到深圳亦應被限制為一周一行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n帶多d貨落去見毛主席啦<br />\n走得一轉架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aebc9ab854ca3703b520d7e3f061ce254f1194d","tid":911013,"uid":47819,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:44:03.000Z","msg":"死得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49361445a208ba3bf59c7de691643ac8f4ca1bb3","tid":911013,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:46:26.000Z","msg":"屌你冇數據9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0f3d5fff2f1cd0ee924cae3312a9ae603c0acf","tid":911013,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd302c190392b369eedd28293941abc176d72b78","tid":911013,"uid":63452,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T16:14:08.000Z","msg":"我淨係知佢有癌症基因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407ab6ea6636f5f74873330305477e67bb0c02dd","tid":911013,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T16:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e31981cd78e4d5ace4f9eadc1bed865a16572ac","t